textbox_5.text: There were multiple strategies. The color darkness always played some importance. The same colors and opponency also did. But what I noticed was that after the test tasks the weighing changed. So there were times when I focused more on saturation and other times more about the opponency axes.
textbox_7.text: About the attention checks, I had this doubt if I missed something because it was always on the positive(+1 to +4).
